        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "苔丝温馨提示：",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 2,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "为了获得更好的体验，游玩该个人故事前，推荐分析员优先观看《合题诗篇》",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 3,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "薄日西垂，街道两旁的商店亮起了灯。今天是和苔丝举行恒约仪式后的第二天，她想出来走走，我自然没有不依的道理。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 4,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "哎，这里是……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 5,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "一家礼服店？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 6,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "啊……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 7,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "怎么了？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 8,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "唔……想起那个晚上了……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 9,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "于是，她挽着我的手，和我讲起之前的事情。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那是几个月之前的事了。但她现在回想，却好像就在昨天——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "同样的黄昏。街道两旁的商店亮起了灯，回家的行人说说笑笑。傍晚的风微凉，红发的姑娘裹紧了衣裳。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "分析员……分析员！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嘿嘿！待会儿就见到分析员了！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "他肯定没料到我能提前赶回来！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 15,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不过……毕竟是分析员，万一真猜到了呢？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 16,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "哼哼，所以才要赶在一天结束的时候……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 17,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "——以为我赶不回来了，我再盛大登场~",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 18,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "啊，天气真不错。晚上约分析员出来散个步吧！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她雀跃着，奔跑的步伐又欢脱了几分。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "然而，脚步骤然停住了。她退了两步，转过身，看着面前的橱窗。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 21,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "隔着玻璃，她看见聚光灯打在人偶的身上。人偶身上的衣物点缀着碎钻，在聚光灯的照耀下星星点点地闪着。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 22,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那是一件恒约礼服。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 23,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "屋檐下的灯有点反光，她不自觉地凑近了玻璃，仔细打量着这件恒约礼服。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 24,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不知道她在想什么，但她看了好久。直到太阳终于完全沉没了，天边只剩下几道残霞，她还是伫立在橱窗前。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 25,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "叮铃——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 26,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "门上的铃铛摇晃——老板注意到了她，推开门走了出来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 27,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "女老板",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "客人，要不要进来看看——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 28,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "女老板",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "诶？人呢？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 29,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "门前一个人也没有。老板揉了揉眼睛，以为自己眼花了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 30,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她挠了挠头，走回了店里。而在不远处的拐角，苔丝正扶着墙喘着气。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 31,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "呼……呼……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 32,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她摸了摸滚烫的脸颊，不知道是因为运动还是因为什么别的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 33,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "走出街角，她又回头看了一眼那家恒约礼服店，然后才慢慢往基地的方向去了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 34,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "天色渐晚，她的步调也越来越慢。海姆达尔基地就在眼前了，她却停了下来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 35,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "呜……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 36,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她捂着脸，原地蹲了下来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 37,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "怎么办……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 38,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "好想穿啊……！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 39,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "基地的轮廓已经隐没在夜色中。有几扇窗还亮着灯。她看向属于playername的那扇窗，灯还亮着。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 40,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "里芙，芬妮，辰星，肴……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 41,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她扳着指头，数出了四个人。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 42,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "里芙……里芙是瓦尔基里冠军，这很合理……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 43,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "芬妮。唉，芬妮那么耀眼，怎么都合理吧？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 44,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "姬辰星……家世又好，能力又强，分析员的左右手……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 45,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "肴曾经是军方的精英，又跟分析员几次出生入死……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 46,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 47,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我只是会点魔术，和其他队友比起来也没什么突出的地方……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 48,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不行不行，分析员会感到为难的！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 49,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "也许分析员还没打算走到那一步……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 50,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "也许、也许——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 51,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "也许这是我的魔术师？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 52,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "啊！分析员！什么时候——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 53,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我猜到苔丝可能会提前赶回来。以我对苔丝的了解，日头未落的黄昏大概是魔术师心目中的最佳登场时间。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 54,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "静谧的下午对她来说有些仓促，夜晚的时机又不够恰到好处。所以我一直在等她。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 55,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "远远地，就看见她幽幽地“飘”过来，就差把“我有心事”四个大字写在脸上了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 56,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在楼上看见你，就下来接你了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 57,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "怎么这么郁闷？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 58,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "锵锵！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 59,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她忽然原地转了一圈，身后亮起一束绚烂的火花。她扑进我的怀里，把头埋在我的胸口，抬起头，悄悄打量着我的神情。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 60,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "唬到分析员了！嘿嘿！这个凯旋魔术怎么样？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 61,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "很不错。烟花是什么时候点的我一点儿都没注意到。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 62,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "想吃什么？我刚好没吃晚饭，一起吧？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 63,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "诶——分析员果然猜到了我会提前回来吧！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 64,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "明明是给我留了肚子，但嘴上却说刚好没吃~",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 65,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这都被你看出来了？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 66,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "哼哼，魔术师的基本功啦~",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 67,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "唔……鹅肝饺子！就决定吃这个了！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 68,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "行，我去安排。你先回房间休整一下，准备好了我再叫你。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 69,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "好耶！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 70,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "脸侧被她轻啄了一下，随后她便雀跃着离开了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 71,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但我却察觉到了一丝微妙。或者说，已经确认了某个事实。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 72,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "——她确实有心事，想要隐瞒的心事。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 73,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "比起平时的相处，她微妙地多了一点点主动和大胆。加上魔术表演和一天没见的期待，几乎成功掩饰了那句话——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 74,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "苔丝绮幻",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "唬到分析员了！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 75,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "（想要开口，又咽下去了……是有话要说？）",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 76,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "想来想去，大概率是和我有关了。",
        "disable": 0
